      <developer_comments>NOTE: There is a rule which the order must follow with one exception.  The rule is that &#34;Mail&#34; and &#34;News&#34; accounts are listed first, then the &#34;Local Folders&#34; account, and finally &#34;Newsgroup&#34; accounts.  The one exception is that the default account is always listed first.

WARNING: If you are using version 0.0.2 and see the message &#34;58: fpAM.getAccount(accounts[i]).incomingServer has no properties&#34; when you open the options window, please click Cancel for the window titled &#34;Folderpane Tools Options&#34;.  Please upgrade to version 0.0.3 to avoid this bug.  To those who have been affected by this bug, please send me an email so I can help you recover your accounts.</developer_comments>
