  <summary>Moves the toolbar back above the tabbar.</summary>
  <description>Moves the toolbar for mails back up above the tabbar. Note that this might cause the design to suffer when using a theme not supporting this extsion. So the default theme has issues with aero on windows (and looks as terrible as it looked before the changes in 1.11).

Note that additional custom toolbars might still go into the tab, and tabs still do have toolbars other than the toolbar for mails (like the calendar when &lt;a href=&#34;https://addons.mozilla.org/thunderbird/addon/lightning/&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; is installed). I personally use it with my theme &lt;a href=&#34;https://addons.mozilla.org/thunderbird/addon/ignore-aero/?src=external-riseofthetools&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;Ignore Aero&lt;/a&gt; on windows, to prevent the aero glitch to reappear.</description><license>
