      <developer_comments>Go get the buttons, do the following:
&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Right-click the toolbar&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Choose Customize...&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Search the button(s)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drag it to the place on the toolbar you want it&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Close the customize-window&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;
